<title>USA: Vivus holders approve 2-for-1 stock split.</title>
<headline>Vivus holders approve 2-for-1 stock split.</headline>
<dateline>MENLO PARK, Calif. 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Vivus Inc said Friday its stockholders approved a two-for-one stock split at the annual meeting Thursday.</p>
<p>The split is payable on or about June 23, record June 2.</p>
<p>The company said all other proposals in the proxy statement were approved at the meeting, and all directors standing for election were re-elected.</p>
